[normal]beeth
[normal]” said for booth, 
[normal]“
[normal]Cheeder
[normal]” for Tudor, “
[normal]Cheeb
[normal]” 
[normal]for 
[normal]   
[normal]Tube, “
[normal]dath
[normal]” for death and “
[normal]teem(
[normal]b)” for tomb.
